  "title": "Sales Director",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description: </strong></p><ul><li>Develop sales strategies and chart direction for sales growth and market expansion</li><li>Set and meet targets for company growth – Sales, Profit, Inventory, Collection</li><li>Establish strong customer relationships to understand customer needs and provide tailored solutions</li><li>Nurture and maintain long-term partnership with key customers or distributors</li><li>Leadership and team development to coach and motivate staff</li><li>Top management engagement with customers and business divisions</li><li>Lead and manage company resources effectively to achieve company KPIs</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirement: </strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Sales & Marketing or Business Management or equivalent</li><li>Exercise judgement in management issues across company level</li><li>Leadership to lead and motivate staff</li><li>Good understanding of company process and system</li><li>Effective communication and coaching skills</li><li>Good grasp of market trends, landscape changes, competitive movements, etc</li><li>10 years of relevant work and business experience</li><li>Strong networking capabilities</li><li>Proficient in spoken and written Japanese</li></ul>",
